data.description: Stunning pool home for sale in Palm Coast! This is truly the entertainers masterpiece with added privacy! Enjoy the large screened in pool with a very spacious backyard patio next to undeveloped land.  The kitchen features an open-floor plan to the living room and is fully upgraded with granite countertops, custom cabinets, and stainless steel appliances! Feel at ease with a nearly brand NEW ROOF and HVAC unit! Observe and enter the beautiful backyard from 2 large sliding doors throughout the home and French doors from the kitchen! Enjoy a roundabout driveway with a 2-car garage! Within very close proximity to major grocery shores and restaurants! There are so many lovely features about this home! Come view 8 Palmer Ln today and fall in love!
